sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant LG as LangGraph (Python App)
    participant OL as Ollama Server
    participant M as Model (Qwen2.5)
    participant T as Tool (Python Function)

    U->>LG: "What is 25 * 4?"
    LG->>OL: Send messages + tool schema
    OL->>M: Forward prompt
    M-->>OL: tool_call(calculator, {"expression":"25*4"})
    OL-->>LG: Return tool_call

    LG->>T: Execute calculator("25*4")
    T-->>LG: "100"

    LG->>OL: Send tool result (role=tool, content="100")
    OL->>M: Continue conversation
    M-->>OL: Final answer text
    OL-->>LG: Assistant response
    LG-->>U: "The result is 100."

    